data.description: Two-story home nestled on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood! Endless possibilities for renovation and expansion. Situated off the Sheridan/92nd Ave exit off US-36. The huge backyard is perfect for outdoor entertaining, and ample space for gardening as well as extra RV parking space. This is a blank canvas waiting for a creative vision. Whether you're an investor seeking a promising venture or a homeowner looking to craft your dream residence, this property offers the space and potential needed. The property is being sold as-is.
